Nigerian billionaire and Forte Oil boss, Femi Otedola, has shared a video of himself prostrating to the Emir of Kano, Muhammad Lamido Sanusi II. The 10-second video showed Otedola in a white attire paying homage by prostrating to Sanusi who was dressed in his royal attire seated and smiling at the humble gesture. The oil tycoon shared the video on his Instagram handle with the caption, “This evening paying homage to the Emir of Kano, Sanusi II.” While many Nigerians believe this gesture to be noble, others opinionate that it is bizarre. Watch video below  This evening paying homage to the Emir of Kano, Sanusi II ⚔️... F.Ote$ A post shared by  Femi Ote💲 (@femiotedola) on Mar 15, 2018 at 1:58pm PDT